        "weeklyRent": 150,
        "peopleInHouse": 2,
        "wouldRecommend": "YES",
        "comment": "I had worked through OrangeJobs in a printing production company in the Netherlands, and it was one of the best jobs I had while working in the country.The company was small, with around 25 employees, and we work in two shifts. The atmosphere was really good and much more relaxed compared to big warehouses. The accommodation provided by the agency was very good, and getting to work was easy on bike. For workplaces over 10 km away, the agency can also provide a car. The job itself was not very complicated, and after a short time it became easy to get used to. The salary was good and payments were always on time. Communication with the coordinator was excellent, she was always helpful and available, even on weekends. I can recommend this agency from the bottom of my heart. Everything worked smoothly and my experience was very positive and definitely would go back to.",
        "issueTags": "[]",
        "verificationStatus": "WORKER_REPORTED",
        "sourceType": "WORKER_REPORTED",
        "createdAt": "2026-03-31T13:10:24.374"
      },
